---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Newsletter from '../components/Newsletter.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Jason Krebs" description="About Jason Krebs — cozy fantasy author.">
  <main>
    <h1>About Jason Krebs</h1>
    <p class="tagline">Cozy fantasy author. Tea drinker. Defender of tired characters.</p>

    <p>
      Jason Krebs writes cozy fantasy about tired people, warm rooms, and
      found families. He drinks more tea than coffee, lives somewhere drafty
      with too many houseplants, and believes the best stories start with
      someone opening a door.
    </p>

    <p>
      <strong>The Crossroads Inn</strong> is his debut series — six novels
      about Briar Thornheart, an ex-mercenary who inherits a magical inn at
      the crossroads of five realms and accidentally builds a life there.
      Book 1 is on its way.
    </p>

    <p>
      If you liked <em>Legends & Lattes</em>, <em>Bookshops & Bonedust</em>,
      <em>Can't Spell Treason Without Tea</em>, or <em>The Very Secret Society
      of Irregular Witches</em>, Jason hopes you'll feel at home at the
      Crossroads Inn.
    </p>

    <hr />

    <Newsletter />

